thread.title: Marilyn Roberts
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Marilyn Roberts

author: Marilyn Roberts
title: Marilyn Roberts
text: Omega did not have a desk at the airport, but we called when we arrived and within a couple of minutes we were picked up and taken to their depot. Service was fast and efficient, the staff helpful. We were dropped back to the airport after returning the car. No problems.
